      "role": "user",
      "content": "those are okay, i guess, but they're kind of generic. i mean, i want stuff that tells me more about who they are as a person. like, we all spend a lot of time hanging out after work or on weekends, doing stuff like skiing or grabbing drinks at certain spots. i need to know if they'll actually vibe with us socially, not just work-wise. can you give me some more personal questions that help filter for that kind of lifestyle match?",
